      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im feeling really weird tonight. my chest feels super heavy, like someone is sitting on it, and i feel kind of sick to my stomach. im also just exhausted, like i cant even move. i know i have bad anxiety and i've had panic attacks like this before, but it feels a bit different this time. do u think its just a bad anxiety spike or something else??",
