      "role": "user",
      "content": "it does feel like i've had before, but the feeling in my chest is really intense and it's making me a bit scared. if i just try the breathing and it doesn't work, is there anything else i can take right now to calm down? i have some extra diazepam from my doctor for when things get really bad, would taking an extra pill help settle this \"spike\" faster?",
